Enjoy seamless rental turnovers and show care for the properties you manage.

With Breezeway, you can:

Schedule tasks based on property turnover or frequency
Complete property inspections and include condition, photos and comments

Communicate with your team on specific tasks

descriptionHtml:
Breezeway is the leading property operations and services platform for short-term rental properties.

- Share work with clients to increase owner retention, acquisition, and referrals
- Integrate with dozens of PMS systems and IoT devices to harness data

- Receive task notifications right from your phone or tablet
- Get high-quality work done through customized mobile checklists
- Leverage mobile apps even when you’re offline without Wi-Fi
- Easily share updates, upload pictures, report issues, and leave comments
- Receive all the details of the job before you arrive, including access code, task requirements, and specific property details
